Tracks
-----------------------------
We are welcoming submissions to the Abstracts or Proceedings
Track. All submissions will undergo a peer-review process.

Abstracts Track: extended abstracts should not exceed 3 pages,
including figures and references. Abstracts will be accepted for oral
or poster presentation, and will appear in the book of abstracts only.

Proceedings Track: full papers should have between 8 and 14 pages and
follow the Springer Proceedings format. Accepted full papers will be
presented at the conference and published by Springer. Only previously
unpublished, original submissions will be accepted.

